com.ostrichemulators.semtool.util

Class RDFDatatypeTools

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ostrichemulators.semtool.util.RDFDatatypeTools

  • public class RDFDatatypeTools
extends Object
    This class offers utility methods for converting between Objects and Values, as well as offering the ability to derive data types for RDF entities.
    Author:
    Wayne Warren

      • getDatatype

        public static org.openrdf.model.URI getDatatype(Object val)
        Gets the datatype of the given val. If val is null, returns null. It returns XMLSchema.ANYURI for a URI, XMLSchema.ENTITY for a BNode, and Literal.getDatatype() if it's a literal. If it's not a Value, then it is converted to a Value first, and reprocessed. If we have a literal, but a null datatype, returns XMLSchema.STRING
        Parameters:
        val -
        Returns:
